node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by PIERRE GASLY 🇫🇷 on July 18, 2021 tagging @alphataurif1, and @teamgasly. May be an image of ‎1 person and ‎text that says '‎ALPHATA World H HONDA SCUDERIA س ALPHATAURI dstad EDIFI CASA IC‎'‎‎.

node.text: Gutted.. Puncture with 5 laps to go while running in P9 so we had to do an extra stop😑 Big shame, as I felt we deserved better after a difficult weekend for us. Quite a lot to go through now, and try to come back with more pace in Budapest. Glad to see @maxverstappen1 is ok after such a scary crash.. Thanks to all the crowd who came at the track, it was wild & amazing all weekend.❤️🇬🇧

Como is incredibly beautifuuuul! Lovely time.

node.text: We fought hard today.⚔️ It wasn’t an easy one starting on the soft but we tried our best. P9, and only 4secs from the Top 5, so there are some positives. We will keep working on these small details to do even better in the coming races. The fight continues.

Very good job from the guys, exciting to go racing tomorrow!!

QUALIFIED 6TH!!😁 Another Q3 in the bag.
Great team work after missing FP2, we put some good laps today! Whether it’s wet or dry, it should be an exciting race tomorrow.

node.text: Got my hands on some Honda e:TECHNOLOGY 👍 #PoweredByHonda

Yaaay, proud to launch my first limited edition sunglasses collection with @hawkersco !😎 Been a very fun & cool project from start to the end, and I hope you guys will like them too! Link in bio to check them out.
